mousetweaks: mousetweaks (Mouse Accessibility Enhancements for GNOME)
mousetweaks:
mousetweaks: mousetweaks provides mouse accessibility enhancements for the GNOME 
mousetweaks: desktop, such as performing various clicks without using any hardware 
mousetweaks: button, and has a Pointer Capture panel applet which can hold the 
mousetweaks: mouse until a user released a predefined button.
